CARRIES WITH IT

24:41.063 --> 24:43.100
SOME VERY SPECIAL
STORY MATERIAL.

24:43.190 --> 24:45.648
ON THE Tl/I/lL/GHTZONE NEXT
TIME, VVE OPEN THAT CAN OF PEAS

24:45.693 --> 24:48.481
AND PRESENT A BATTLE BETWEEN
THE MEN AND THE MACHINES.

24:48.570 --> 24:50.652
RICHARD DEACON AND
PAUL NEVVLAN STAR IN

24:50.698 --> 24:52.689
"THE BRAIN CENTER
AT WHIPPLE'S."
